## ğŸ§© 1. Internet vs Web

| Concept                      | Analogy                    | Description                                                        |
| ---------------------------- | -------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| ğŸŒ **Internet**              | The *highway system*       | A global network of computers connected together                   |
| ğŸ•¸ï¸ **World Wide Web (WWW)** | *Cars driving on highways* | A system that uses the internet to share websites, data, and files |

