## ğŸ”’ 3. HTTP vs HTTPS

| Protocol  | Full Form                          | Secure? | Description                                 |
| --------- | ---------------------------------- | ------- | ------------------------------------------- |
| **HTTP**  | HyperText Transfer Protocol        | âŒ       | Basic communication between client & server |
| **HTTPS** | HyperText Transfer Protocol Secure | âœ…       | Encrypted using SSL/TLS (protects data)     |

**Why HTTPS?**

* Without HTTPS, data is visible to hackers ğŸ‘€
* With HTTPS, everything is encrypted ğŸ” â€” like whispering a secret instead of shouting it

