## ğŸ” 4. The Requestâ€“Response Cycle

Hereâ€™s what happens when you open a webpage:

1. ğŸ§­ **DNS Lookup** â€” Finds the IP address of the website (`example.com â†’ 93.184.216.34`)
2. ğŸ“¤ **Browser Sends Request** â€” â€œHey server, give me your homepage!â€
3. ğŸ–¥ï¸ **Server Processes Request** â€” Prepares HTML/data
4. ğŸ“¥ **Server Sends Response** â€” Sends back the page/data
5. ğŸ§¾ **Browser Renders It** â€” You see the page

ğŸ’¡ **Analogy:**
You order food â†’ restaurant cooks it â†’ waiter delivers â†’ you eat.

