## ğŸ§® 8. HTTP Methods (CRUD Mapping)

| Method     | CRUD             | Description         | Example           | Analogy                |
| ---------- | ---------------- | ------------------- | ----------------- | ---------------------- |
| **GET**    | Read             | Retrieve data       | `GET /users`      | â€œShow me the menu ğŸ½ï¸â€ |
| **POST**   | Create           | Send new data       | `POST /users`     | â€œPlace my order ğŸ§¾â€    |
| **PUT**    | Update           | Replace data        | `PUT /users/1`    | â€œChange my orderâ€      |
| **PATCH**  | Update (partial) | Modify part of data | `PATCH /users/1`  | â€œAdd extra cheese ğŸ§€â€  |
| **DELETE** | Delete           | Remove data         | `DELETE /users/1` | â€œCancel my order âŒâ€    |

