## ğŸ§¾ 13. Quick Recap

| Concept              | Summary                                          |
| -------------------- | ------------------------------------------------ |
| **HTTP/HTTPS**       | Communication protocol between client and server |
| **Requestâ€“Response** | Core conversation flow                           |
